text: Alejandro Barrenechea (born 30 March 1976) is a Spanish gymnast. He competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bilbao
